window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Captain Kyle Roberts has commanded the carrier <i>Avalon</i> through the most vicious battles of the war against the Terran Commonwealth - but with <i>Avalon</i> in for repair, his political enemies deny him a new ship. </p> <p>Unwilling to accept a desk, he takes command of a covert operation using a captured Commonwealth warship to strike at the very heart of their enemy, drawing away the reinforcements that could destroy the Alliance's recent gains. </p> <p>But the spies who planned the operation have secrets they haven't shared. Their allies have their own agendas - and the Commonwealth has surprises of its own! </p>"; 
